          <!-- Behavioral -->
          <div class="px-2 m-2 text-3xl font-bold underline" style="width: 96%;">Behavioral Addiciton</div>
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row border-solid border-2 rounded-md shadow-lg p-4 m-4" style="width: 96%;">
            <div class="w-full lg:mt-0 md:w-2/5">
              <img src="images/behavioral.png" alt="behavioral" class="w-full h-full max-w-md mx-auto">
            </div>
            <div class="p-3 md:w-3/5 text-justify text-lg break-words">
              <p>
                The term "behavioral addiction" describes compulsive, repetitive behaviors that people engage in despite
                unfavorable
                effects. Unlike drug addiction, behavioral addictions are characterized by an obsession with a
                particular activity or
                set of behaviors, such as online gaming, shopping, or gambling. These addictions have the potential to
                significantly
                affect a person's personal, social, and professional lives. People may suffer intense cravings, symptoms
                of withdrawal,
                and an inability to restrain or stop their addictive behavior. Understanding the underlying causes of
                behavioral
                addictions and obtaining the proper support and therapy are crucial first steps in managing and
                overcoming these
                difficulties.
              </p>
              <p><span class="font-bold underline">Fact:</span> In 2022, the overall prevalence of behavioral addiction
                irrespective of addiction type
                was 11.1%, the most prevalent being smartphone addiction (contributing more than 30%) <a
                  href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/36118286/#:~:text=A%20total%20of%2094%20studies,CI%3A%205.4%20to%2016.8%25)."
                  target="_blank" class="underline text-[#0000EE]"> (Source)</a></p>
              <p><span class="font-bold underline">Related Links:</span>
              <ul class="list-disc">
                <li>
                  <a href="https://www.addictioncenter.com/addiction/behavioral-addictions/" target="_blank"
                    class="underline text-[#0000EE]">https://www.addictioncenter.com/addiction/behavioral-addictions/</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3354400/" target="_blank"
                    class="underline text-[#0000EE]">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3354400/</a>
                </li>
              </ul>
              </p>
            </div>
